
lets learn about g++ compiler options by exploring codeforces g++ run command :
 GNU C++11 4
 g++.exe  -static 
          -fno-optimize-sibling-calls 
          -fno-strict-aliasing 
          -DONLINE_JUDGE 
          -lm 
          -s 
          -x c++ 
          -Wl,--stack=268435456 
          -O2 
          -std=c++11 
          -D__USE_MINGW_ANSI_STDIO=0 
          -o {filename}.exe {file}

corresponding info at the url : http://codeforces.ru/blog/entry/79 :
